name: WannaUI
summary: WANNA UI SDK enhances your iOS app with 3D Viewer for handbags.
description:
WANNA’s 3D Viewer for handbags was specifically crafted to answer the
industry’s pain point — the high number of returns due to the wrong size of
the bag. It provides users with a novel experience to understand the size and
capacity of a bag and enables brands to showcase the product with the utmost
realism. Such an experience is designed to help clients make an informed
shopping decision by exploring the product's size, dimensions, texture, and
key attributes before purchase.
